metadata.name: Spirited Comeback
metadata.description:
[ENG]
Morning looks unusual...
lost spirit grows back, along with my new way to plant dreams in the sky.
The loss that used to be now begins to be filled by the glow of the soul's flame in the chest.

---------------------------------------------
[IND]
Pagi nampak tak seperti biasanya...
semangat yang hilang tumbuh kembali, bersama dengan caraku yang baru utnuk menanam mimpi-mimpi di langit.
Kehilangan yang dahulu kini mulai terisi oleh pendar nyala api jiwa di dalam dada.

---------------------------------------------

mixed media (cut out paper, editing and finishing by Photoshop)
4000x4000 pixel
300 dpi
